name: PYC Dissasembler
short_description: PYC Dissasembler disassemble python byte compiled files (.pyc) into a series of opcodes. It work for every version of python 2 (that use cpython) but must be run with a good interpreter. Ex: you can only disassemble python 2.7 pyc files with a python 2.7 interpreter.
summary: Disassemble python byte compiled file for python 2.x
